/**
 * src/pages/index.astro  — Hosen Digital Homepage
 *
 * HOW TO EDIT CONTENT
 * ───────────────────
 * All text, links, and data live in the variables below (between the --- fences).
 * Change anything here and the page updates automatically — you never need to
 * touch the HTML markup lower down.
 *
 * Sections you can edit:
 *   site        — <head> metadata (title, description, canonical URL)
 *   nav         — navigation links & CTA label
 *   hero        — badge, headline, sub-copy, CTA buttons, mini-stats
 *   heroCards   — the 6 feature cards in the hero grid
 *   trustedBy   — "Trusted by" strip text & client name list
 *   work        — section heading and the two work/case-study cards
 *   about       — section badge, headline, body paragraphs, overlay blurb
 *   services    — section heading and the 6 service cards
 *   whyUs       — section heading and 4 benefit items
 *   stats       — the 3 stat numbers + labels (dark banner)
 *   process     — section heading and 4 process steps
 *   testimonials— the 3 testimonial cards
 *   faq         — section heading and FAQ accordion items
 *   cta         — main CTA section (email, phone, trust signals)
 *   ctaHotel    — secondary CTA section with image grid
